Starscream struggled with consiousness. He fought it off for awhile 
and stood up, walkng dizzily over to the others. Most of his body was 
completly scorched. He needed help fast.

"Hey Phobia. Glad to see the crash didn't put you under. Now.....how 
are we all doing? Good. Now, as Emperor of the Decepticons, I order 
all of us to make a frontal assault on Optimus Prime. And becareful 
for Earth, he hates me. Jungle Monkey should take the left right, and 
I'll charge around the backwards!"

Starscream collapsed onto the ground again.
